textContent:
---mixue---

Amishu so much bbycakes!!! It's been a while since nag PM shift ka and tulog ka now while I'm writing this. MISS NA MISS NA MISS NA KITAAAAA HUHUHUHU. I can't wait to see you tomorrow at last!! Grabe huhuhu, nagkaka sepanx talaga ako huhu. Super pagod nanaman at work kaya di ko maiwasan na mamiss ka talaga kase ikaw yung instant power bank ko lagi bby huhu. MWAAAAA. I hope you're sleeping well today my love!

---job hunt---

Thank you sa pagiging supportive lagi sa job hunt ko atm!! Kabadong kabado ako lagi pero your words and presence really calm me down! I hope na by the time na nababasa mo to, may matinong job offer nakooo (malabo tho, pero sana mag dilang anghel nalang ako HAHAHAHA). Para may pambili na tayo ng cute and estetik na furniture sa bahay natennn. Talagang yon agad naiisip ko. Yon na talaga motivation ko ngayon para yumaman: our future together.

---bff---

Wala lang, naisip ko lang bigla na bff na talaga kita hahaha. Naalala ko kase bigla yung sinend ko na reel sayo about how I protected my peace too much kaya ikaw nalang kaibigan ko HAHAHAHA. That is so me!! Pero dw! I wouldn't have it any other way. I'm always happy to spend all my time with you kaya I'm very happy with how open we are with each other kase that makes spending our time together so much easier! I love you bby!!
